OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThere will often be large
OL,6,Famounts of cloud, but still bright and
OL,7,Fperhaps sunny spells will occur with
OL,8,Fall areas remaining dry. It will feel
OL,9,Fwarm in the light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry and becoming largely
OL,12,Fclear, although low cloud may creep
OL,13,Facross western areas, especially
OL,14,FDerbyshire where a little drizzle may
OL,15,Fdevelop over the Peak District.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
