OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FCloudy, with morning patchy
OL,6,Fdrizzle or light rain across the Peak
OL,7,FDistrict and with hill fog lifting.
OL,8,FElsewhere sunny start for most places,
OL,9,Fthen becoming largely cloudy. Warm.
OL,10,FBreezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,13,FGenerally large amounts of cloud,
OL,14,Falthough some bright or sunny spells
OL,15,Fwill occur, especially Sunday.
OL,16,FOccasionally breezy, and becoming warm
OL,17,For very warm as temperatures are
OL,18,Flikely to gradually increase.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
